To set up and run tests in the spec/ direcory, install Jasmine:

 npm install -g jasmine
 jasmine init
 jasmine examples

Then run:
  jasmine

But jasmine alone sucks ass. Can't set source files?

 npm install -g karma
 npm install -g karma-phantomjs-launcher --save-dev
 karma init
 karma start



 npm install karma-jquery --save-dev


 npm install -g bower
 bower install jquery-ui



Also potentially useful is Yeoman to build scaffolding, though so far it's annoying too
 npm install -g yo
 npm install -g generator-karma
 yo karma
